# test_asterisk
: Test table with asterisk substitution in column names
- *_id int *pk
: Column where * is replaced with table name (test_asterisk_id)
- user_* int k1
: Column with * at end (user_test_asterisk)
- *_middle_* varchar50
: Column with multiple * (test_asterisk_middle_test_asterisk)
- \*_literal varchar20
: Column with escaped asterisk (\* becomes literal *)
- count_\* int
: Column with escaped asterisk at end
